Impeachment and NFL criticismWhat about the idea Democrats wanted to impeach Trump for criticizing the NFL?
Our ratingGallagher claimed that the Dec. 18 House impeachment vote was the third by Democrats — "They tried to impeach Trump for criticizing the NFL and for some other things."
The three roll call votes he referred to weren’t impeachment votes — they were procedural votes to set aside debate on impeachment measures.